<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f5f2;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background: rgb(72, 116, 151);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #f4f817;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #000000;
            text-align: justify;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Our Restaurant</h1>

        <p>
            Welcome to our restaurant! Since our beginning, we have been dedicated
            to serving delicious meals prepared with fresh ingredients and passion.
            Our mission is to provide customers with a warm atmosphere, excellent
            service, and unforgettable dining experiences.
        </p>

        <p>
            We believe food brings people together, and every dish we create is
            made with love and care. Thank you for being a part of our journey.
        </p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>